{ --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4fd99cae-d049-461e-93e1-392d0a219976\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a24d9a3-cca0-4ebf-9c39-1ceb65c221ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">브랜드의 첫인상을 결정짓는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5b4bee37-68a1-425a-b017-f28f60fa8b1c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9ab71a4-4ebe-47ea-89e3-26ac7c831f82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">핵심 요소, 바로 '패키지 디자인'이죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f76c5219-7ce5-41b9-948d-c0516acf31cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5c4a35f-70df-4034-b543-5a2296aab45b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-70c97805-0086-4d63-af6a-0974d6175904\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-66a6cb13-ffd0-4482-a63a-1e1cfd4eae87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘은 단순히 제품을 안전하게</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b912d877-dc1f-4b74-8ac1-c72f8bf9a5b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3356901-d3f2-4a94-933c-58b627dee12c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">배송하는 것을 넘어, 고객이 택배 상자를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c52a8b21-afec-4dcf-b944-a7013b994f5f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fa488392-5f6b-417e-b1ea-463354633375\" style=\"color:#555555;\">열었을 때 느끼는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6cbb72e6-67b8-4e2e-adec-2db26cfc5aa8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a13d84a4-5a91-4cd4-9258-466fff78992d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">'언박싱(Unboxing) 경험'이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-776aecfb-4f14-4440-90b4-70268c969b1c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-320f57d2-f861-4661-a245-07882bd0b182\" style=\"color:#555555;\">브랜드의 가치를 좌우하곤 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9dc3d612-380e-4cb8-ac7e-fb21b29a1dd1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea89ed87-265d-46b9-a85f-4d40aa403fd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이때 가장 감성적이면서도 고급스러운</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-911e1115-d765-48d0-a04c-5c05cc4aa044\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-48bee225-5e09-47b7-b846-7a3aa791468d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">분위기를 연출할 수 있는 아이템이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-352f6e9f-29cd-490a-a8ed-95570083ab66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea4b2aff-067e-4c51-a3db-632a70f18701\" style=\"color:#555555;\">바로 노루지와 습자지인데요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-bfd2e06c-c6b2-4a09-a25a-722f0f05dd13\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" oncli