-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f182892b-8406-4e86-b44f-6bd80bf0afe6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b835cb1f-1ee3-4e5a-ad5e-8c00bb42dfde\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작 시 주의 사항까지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-598563f0-abe0-4f64-9516-0625211271e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f389901-5431-4276-ae31-704cba808f03\" style=\"color:#555555;\">알짜배기 정보만 모아 정리해 드릴게요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b92b0975-5df4-4a20-b5d6-dd773d58c656\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e9c51b29-e2f6-49a4-bf32-a4e0b551ad18\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-25d56e5f-88b2-4862-bf6e-7f73e7624373\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f8b01c5-dfd2-46f6-b72a-402a18d8e4c7\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">1. 노루지 vs 습자지, 어떻게 다를까?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e8eb213-331c-4626-84c1-d8faacc13a4d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4c2d6f43-49b9-41a0-a8fa-848b086ae0b8\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2dfa4dae-1ad2-4cab-97b9-0f97a8d5e4dd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b54e7c10-9baf-4a95-b723-35584b024655\" style=\"color:#555555;\">두 종이 모두 얇고 비치는 특성이 있어</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cb493f13-d2ce-497b-8715-da5cf0c4afa4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e70f9a41-faa1-4a3e-9735-5006de55e2b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">혼동하기 쉽지만,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ea8da561-7578-47ff-ac39-6dfcc5edaf75\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3187606-d93e-4a8b-8b51-1d6b9687394b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">용도와 재질에 명확한 차이가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-14665a9f-0a2c-4919-8872-b9a4b8e4c01a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-241e73e4-7c05-43bb-9016-fe5c582183f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">우리 브랜드 제품에는 어떤 종이가 맞을지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e3156a4-e340-4800-8446-05061743823e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f74292c-8e88-4563-9d90-d4ec3301bdda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">먼저 비교해 보세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7a5e2a42-bc64-4ec1-80ed-8fd7736439a8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b795248b-9146-452c-b36b-3b33ed453372\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3f33ef64-09ac-4825-b785-bfad248b8cdd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ba781fb-b6a9-461e-9bab-741502d12386\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8dc812a9-e9ad-43ee-bca5-4e78846d4e54\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2453d33-9a47-4133-9144-b494edcb79d3\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 노루지 (Greaseproof / Sulfite Paper)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-95a2a083-2989-42f5-b1c0-eea23f0fd1cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dcf29c70-a42d-4504-b98f-2f99d4ca9bdb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-504ad84b-a3d8-4ad4-b494-6814431b2a8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ec5c5b8b-ed3f-4bc0-8a96-5e7b24ed433b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>특징 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f5ac44dc-a74d-4b27-a2be-759e6442b38d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6970972-2b36-445b-8520-8937854eaca5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">습자지에 비해 상대적으로 질기고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-de0e9c3b-7465-4802-9e59-a176a2fcc18c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b1e1586-bf35-4ca6-a28a-f8e4c8d65bbd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">탄탄하며, 표면이 매끄러운 편입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d0d8f900-5584-498f-9ae0-0b9335a3ce3e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58d892d2-9eeb-492b-8cc7-4d3378932750\" style=\"color:#555555;\">약간의 반투명한 느낌을 주며,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dfa7ea33-2707-497f-9620-7fdd5174d6b1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fe49bf94-374f-4b62-8f04-43168e40a937\" style=\"color:#555555;\">습기와 기름기에 강한 특성이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2c6528ba-98b7-447e-85ef-9c35726e3da6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c30615a-82b1-4bf6-a595-aaa2a83ef8a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-438b2d30-b3b1-4415-b2d2-1a352b355fd4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5a6a94ed-2121-46fc-97fd-94f04a94de6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주요 용도 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8ca723ee-09c8-4c25-a5ed-be1034fa0cfd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be5be06f-5157-4395-95ae-62552d223328\" style=\"color:#555555;\">베이커리·디저트 포장, 의류 및 잡화 포장,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d704f3fe-755b-4faf-a670-54d987303f89\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39f9e041-ddc9-4442-a3af-eb38d0ad6b74\" style=\"color:#555555;\">꽃다발 속지, 고급 식품 포장 등.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-25a6e0a7-bec6-4eae-aa76-437fe6b648e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9bcbba61-e40f-43db-bee1-1fb72e880b25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-83b91b65-2aa9-4088-84d1-332ebf56de8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-79fd5e79-b7c8-48db-a188-31a084f62ed3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>추천 브랜드 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-05f84524-23bd-49fc-808d-b54e23830432\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6655fa1-799a-444f-b43a-b24c736350d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">깔끔하고 각이 잡힌 포장이나, 기름기가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-24913511-a7d6-4d5a-9410-b2489c5fbaf0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5c1ed0d-99e9-4c2e-b9f6-ed34b2e16b62\" style=\"color:#555555;\">묻어날 수 있는 식품류를 취급하는 브랜드.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db870904-7571-4a75-a254-94f0e12df8e2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9bdb89e3-e0b3-4650-8e72-afcbddd2779f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224289319499/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c661860-4dc0-408d-a79a-fe45ffda27b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03fbbd89-d132-4dca-a5d3-4a83cef1a927\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ebff3ea7-a1a3-4c08-823a-14b0ca1b88d8\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">□ 습자지 (Tissue Paper)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c4a8c7e4-314e-4938-8d6e-9dd44caa5f04\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4c82664-f030-44de-a86c-d6c236d35b38\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2ca62201-1cfe-4dca-b79f-78a5b0734630\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7c8f1ffd-dc82-45d3-af4d-b040703ee177\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>특징 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-366ffa74-57f5-48fb-b553-00439ee6901d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cfc6c508-7cda-4d0e-a5e7-aa190a7b7efb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">매우 얇고 바스락거리는 부드러운 촉감이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b8f95295-06c4-4ed2-8918-e7cd8b202fe5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ec54cda-511a-4bdd-b8d9-bfdf098675aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특징입니다. 수분을 흡수하는 성질이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5326730a-2ce7-40cd-a173-8f067ed945e3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-145b78b2-4428-492a-a0b4-b0eebba9e8aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">뛰어나며, 제품 간의 마찰을 줄여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9265e2ca-86a1-4511-b73e-7947346ae5d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-355b4862-c64b-44e6-ac03-ecf357ba2e46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스크래치를 방지해 줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-706cc7f3-0863-434c-a83c-baeeae92846d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd06355c-efad-4cc5-8f70-78978e66815f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-01f4cffc-4116-483f-997a-0c4377c5b0e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6408282-c431-4cf8-b00e-af83626756b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>주요 용도 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5b81b8eb-adcd-4b96-8532-c69ad0e11b8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-421bd71a-d20b-44eb-843b-3d3b3c198d66\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의류(셔츠, 니트 등) 포장 내지,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1b08e4bb-182c-4803-98b7-d6c3f9ce7ed0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4baf2885-fed3-492c-a48d-a7849d4ec73e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">구두·가방 등 피혁 제품 충전재 및</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-21ee77f0-f204-4380-ae02-8fec0e103a9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f75647ab-4db9-4cc9-b31f-23137bf4a54f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">감싸기용, 명품 패키지 속지 등.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04a400cc-51f8-4f52-a869-f74514d1aaa9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-242e25ab-fe1d-4919-9aa4-a367b19c9a22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-63ab2ad2-deab-44dc-9b63-4da054a849b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e58d79c6-8d61-4551-8ff8-1e03d45aae33\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>추천 브랜드 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9abd7abb-8f6f-48c9-a6dc-8cb2aa845de2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9079bb75-159b-4372-8f3b-44ecf10ed77e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고급스러운 실루엣을 연출하고 싶거나,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ef8604f2-d642-4ab8-b5d1-2f3a83198be2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0160e07-5648-4aa5-950e-1a338ea35bac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">습기에 취약한 의류·가죽 제품을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a50a201c-1aef-4368-90d1-e216b30c0b2e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e50e05dc-8727-4d1d-8d3d-5e9177656fa5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">취급하는 브랜드.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e8afd34c-3849-4a16-afb3-308d7b78475c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-176cc2ab-0a41-4498-9fa8-d9ff79da783d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ea070e72-6eae-44e7-ad46-7eebd27c0f0e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54de36ef-9945-4976-9b38-d82849eb20f6\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">2. 맞춤 로고 인쇄가 사랑받는 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a98e0b2f-726b-4f15-8d55-3fb6510473d4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c7ea15a-b6d5-4846-abcf-ebbb17df9d4b\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5521722a-06b8-40e8-ab25-b95e93a53cb1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-550607f0-4c2e-4f9a-8eee-9dbaa579ea40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">무지(無地) 종이로 포장하는 것도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0ce2d1a4-b036-432e-b369-9cbe78cbbe45\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e6ec73db-61a9-4aa6-9633-cb05d783f9d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">깔끔하지만, 브랜드의 로고나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a47daefa-5f06-4310-a7ae-5bbce0639ebf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f34e2f3e-07f0-40ea-9268-1b55becb7cfc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시그니처 패턴을 인쇄했을 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0d8a6e0d-11dc-4575-9ffd-bf26481df234\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cac38152-f6a1-476e-be63-6882bd1dda9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시너지 효과는 엄청납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b53990a0-8745-437e-8b89-33c913253ed3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47e862f2-c5d7-49f9-b017-429bd0a3b5c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a83be46a-1bb0-4cb5-b781-32598442302f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e1f3f075-15a7-4085-93c2-d2674d1769b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>감성적인 브랜딩 효과 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-78b017ad-15d7-4d3c-912f-3e807990c359\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-abd47303-a8f9-417d-aaff-920609d39f4b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정성스럽게 감싸진 로고 인쇄지를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-559875d8-e87d-4cac-a957-00368b7e8ac4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9bdc6da-0586-494c-a8d6-67745980ae1b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보는 순간, 고객은 '대접받는 느낌'을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-426aee5c-4fc6-41b5-a842-0d2646579904\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fecb0d88-523b-4fe8-8021-618c9d36c0a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">받게 되며 브랜드의 전문성을 인지합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7e90efc7-3b20-42ae-ab45-c786a8541dba\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ad97b8fb-1a02-42a9-9a19-3d02a4341a4a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ec6eca84-515d-47f0-8eb8-06b2521fa60a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7572397b-9055-4cdf-8f09-ae849aa4645f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>가성비 최고의 마케팅 :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-72a40375-aa7d-4f92-9ad7-ea3ae8c82334\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92bc062c-81d0-4d28-b273-4964fb759d12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박스 자체를 제작하는 것보다,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-03c91872-0744-4b7e-893a-b615827d9c1c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f9d5ec5-36ad-450d-99fe-d774308a2454\" style=\"color:#555555;\">얇은 속지에 인쇄를 하는 것이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3754ea19-bcf1-4497-bf82-cffdcf1d4c90\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6fd0025-5f62-45a5-b950-5d10ad7b038a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">비용 대비 시각적 만족도가 매우 높습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4dc2e3c2-5d1d-4f11-bde6-72d458ca89be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a530b799-e724-49cd-b467-9e71bdd6d7b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-05e711fb-65b0-4e02-8b4a-30e372b30e87\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-97e99181-1888-4748-9b1e-e0960909226c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인스타그래머블(Instagrammable) :</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bf50f7b0-f5a2-428d-a6cc-c21f90d2dbaf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7559949-e114-491e-89b7-576e21b712a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예쁜 패키지는 고객의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04744584-048c-4607-8e00-d8f070a1caa8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e586a6d-1b8e-4fa1-924b-16de494738ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자발적인 SNS 인증샷을 유도하여</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-29bddabe-7adc-4bbe-ae7a-8bd60d28f7a6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5972917d-4b59-4242-8aac-dff8f0ace055\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자연스러운 홍보 효과를 가져옵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d096a7a5-d1aa-40b5-8f7d-1faa9ef5085a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-64309d98-27c5-4dde-9ef3-d66da37040eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9e84430c-5b7e-4f76-97e2-70481f793f91\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6264f77e-54ad-453b-8fb4-8fdb0968b50d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-864e301a-0111-40ec-884b-dcad9c20f40b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-12a05925-4083-430d-9755-bc3ff534e7f9\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">3. 성공적인 노루지/습자지 인쇄를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-eac1fbcc-3a2b-404e-9872-1c38a6724ad4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8872f98-8de9-45fa-815e-0dde9f535c9f\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">위한 체크리스트</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e24c37d6-b597-4b3e-8b65-e74f50a01564\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2727bd7-69dc-4ddb-bf0a-3cf6e379c6c0\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-95f5c5b9-d16c-4753-900a-b9ef5109f388\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b860024-7233-4cf0-b11b-08b39396d02f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이가 워낙 얇기 때문에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8a0f080d-0aad-4cb5-afb3-e10a21d38229\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-269ab761-e4e9-4a45-88ec-979fb607c9bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반 용지 인쇄와는 다른 접근이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4b1be627-6324-4a0c-8d4b-5a131b6a9ee7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8418c187-7839-4104-9a40-832a0eb8b30e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-07fa6f5a-e929-4e25-84b5-a0f83ce69d1e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a14ffc1-ae5e-4976-88f4-020d7c3dbf4a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작 실패를 줄이는 3가지 팁을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-443a97e9-013c-4ec9-9641-a8e4b63916c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c699cbf8-3ff0-4248-871e-e098790ab641\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기억하세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-16d170a9-2550-4d08-b637-211d3c5386e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4e52483-8242-4a16-9bda-4f349a4bab07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-559f859c-694a-4a72-903b-6e58569d86ad\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c538ad04-5e3d-4e16-8b50-1da5cb9d004d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>·  평량(두께) 선택이 핵심</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7784e814-8583-4654-8d1b-269ba1a6620a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8d2435db-9c29-498c-b57d-ceb4e76f81e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">습자지는 보통 14g~17g의 초박엽지가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-42ae157c-e54f-4224-99e3-0869151c366e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca8ecf1c-2aae-4134-992a-f2c30364989b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 많이 쓰이며, 조금 더 두꺼운 느낌을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d247751b-fa76-4642-905b-22a882bcfc66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bdb3927e-0e6d-4f26-a45b-2812fc15d095\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원하시면 20g 이상을 선택합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ab2c6d1a-af28-4d02-90f6-f0cbbc91a699\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7f307ed4-3a98-4409-b6e9-97aa60049ec5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-05845366-51b1-4345-bfea-528409b666b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b93a23b-b8eb-4152-bd00-470445d332d9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">노루지는 주로 23g~35g 사이에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-924b3272-3e2f-40bd-8f37-d4477d952198\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07f8bbdf-c02d-4429-982b-fd2fcdf1f7f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작되며, 두꺼워질수록 비침이 적고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7628e52b-3474-47b6-9d94-9c8e20d78ed5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d13a9cdb-a7d9-4057-99b7-f3cafc51d8cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">빳빳해집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-63570f3f-0e77-4361-85d9-da2277dec3df\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5cec10eb-fce7-4c00-98e5-2e61c402faf6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ef5f05e7-2a02-4988-b69d-8b56eb3e4e3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-326187ef-9001-4b0a-8244-207ec959e315\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 평량에 따라 차이를 일반인은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7af11a1b-05b9-4c85-be52-5588ddbb8b2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7225be83-23cc-4630-b60a-f40652c308c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거의 느끼지 못합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dd639dfd-6c2d-4544-bf45-1c385eb73c69\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c21fa716-b6ff-4670-9130-7434456d142c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 추천하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-85330ed3-d9fe-4aa0-b14d-63e8581a7395\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8ee4735-6847-4642-b068-933638e67b38\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일반적인 평량으로 진행하시는 것이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c49e871f-6994-4caa-b708-829c7a0477e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e572090a-25db-4bad-a566-053176465f9d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-259ecd88-b45c-4729-8f38-a5c04cf0bd5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-365ea40a-39b3-427a-86fb-d2a6fe365582\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bd90da4d-5a87-440a-a586-4b966e5d8074\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7134d993-363c-46cf-b5dc-b5ba1c4437bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>·  디자인은 '1도 인쇄'와 '패턴'을 추천</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1903457f-0a87-42ae-8b07-221ec3cfef16\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-103f3257-91ee-4509-b861-96c16b04d2fb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a3bdc88-fae8-4f1a-9f7d-ffd24d9aac83\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이가 얇아 잉크를 많이 먹는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-615fa836-e1da-4436-a171-9762cbaac43f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c9bd911-508d-4071-b320-4004e1315001\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대면적 인쇄(전면 색상 깔기)는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b29ae7b4-6afa-43ec-a8e5-4382bdebb698\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-abc49bc1-595f-4a61-928d-826485eb4e11\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이가 우글거리거나 뒷면에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-eabae604-9c37-4542-be77-9db224f65557\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2f7767f-11a2-418b-8ddc-4977f8fa8f57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">심하게 배어 나올 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-66d79c8b-9f5e-4eb9-b8ab-3c890c4a0f4b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71b5649f-9bd7-4324-94f9-67236893af2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ea691c76-3682-4472-be39-195221b9af25\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b743598-8d91-452b-9480-34c7b7bf9030\" style=\"color:#555555;\">화이트, 블랙, 그레이, 혹은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-96684589-14e7-4f75-a2eb-41808b10b850\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ffd54ea0-1750-4add-829b-0bb23a9f1b10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">브랜드의 시그니처 컬러 1가지(1도)를</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ad75401d-0f6e-4111-aea9-4e13e36655c6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-03abc81a-0d05-4061-afa8-afa1c28f37cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">활용해 로고를 일정한 간격으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f76802ce-3f61-4210-ae32-2048f6c78381\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8605f1d-a5e0-4bd3-87cf-ef366c1d8791\" style=\"color:#555555;\">배합한 '바둑판 패턴(사선 패턴)' 디자인이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b5903c6b-0848-4bb6-89b9-b131452647d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d81cb70-a0b6-4d16-a8b1-16d9acabae05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 깔끔하고 예쁘게 인쇄됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cf254eb6-93aa-4ee7-b489-1f934c628d60\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdced20c-a0c9-42e6-a130-ba09129ac8e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7c3ba73a-5c7f-4e0e-9b15-9da6f560f038\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25c9a40e-35df-452e-b3c9-252dfa0c60ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄 관련해서는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cf1891b0-66e0-4082-9730-b81685c86d7f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-55f22bac-ad34-4ad1-85b0-f15a53ace0d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">반드시 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d1f970d-a5cf-4aa2-b49d-3c37383b62e4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecb79c81-c073-4447-8cc2-7d64f234d2bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-af105e8b-906f-4544-ae30-43b49a1c3bf2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a13fcf8c-b9c6-42c1-9ced-9eec8d8ef69a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>·  최소 제작 수량(MOQ) 확인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-61d75cdb-ce80-4204-bb91-1ed9e02c3def\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1bc1df9-34fe-485c-90d8-a42486e8007e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">얇은 종이 인쇄는 특수 롤 장비나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ae8b4abd-6af4-4ad2-904c-5fe3e0fdd961\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06273e4a-d95f-4632-9989-7e97ed6e00d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정밀한 공정이 필요하여 기성품과</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-76d8d941-1f77-4603-aaf4-8f8cb8360764\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3fed7d87-f874-442b-bddf-fb1a750c9cfb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">달리 최소 수량</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-520092cf-7310-480c-b941-cd3678fe2818\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dcfd55b8-cd54-4b0b-a149-0acd5d3beb0d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(예 : 1,000매 또는 1Rall 단위 등)이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-cbebc6a8-e167-4b15-8573-64cb38cded45\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d56f2c8-ca37-490b-a232-ea896496c146\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정해져 있는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c765f4fe-da20-48d2-8f89-8b75798b38bf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04081885-1379-4745-b5b5-c131c7399984\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제작 전 인쇄 업체와 수량 상담은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c3b02244-50bc-4cf5-9ac4-ec146e75afa5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7299e0c5-2f82-4175-a749-d3800262c624\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필수입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-822a7a4b-cd75-4a9b-a50d-29e68f13181e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224289319499/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}